[ACTIVITY] 訂單結帳流程（Chain B — 分支，共用 API）
[ACTOR] 買家 -> {specs/actors/買家.md}
[ACTOR] 系統 -> {specs/actors/系統.md}
[ACTOR] 金流服務 -> {specs/actors/金流服務.md}
[ACTOR] 倉庫 -> {specs/actors/倉庫.md}

[INITIAL]
[STEP:1] @買家 {specs/features/A03-訂單/001-購物車.dsl.feature}
[STEP:2] @買家 {specs/features/A03-訂單/002-結帳付款.dsl.feature}
[DECISION:2a] 付款方式
  [BRANCH:2a:信用卡]
    [STEP:2a.1] @金流服務 {specs/commands/信用卡扣款.feature}
    [DECISION:2a1] 扣款結果
      [BRANCH:2a1:成功]
        [STEP:2a1.1] @系統 {specs/commands/建立訂單.feature}
      [BRANCH:2a1:失敗]
        [STEP:2a1.2] @買家 {specs/ui/顯示付款失敗.md}
    [MERGE:2a1]
  [BRANCH:2a:超商]
    [STEP:2a.2] @系統 {specs/commands/建立超商訂單.feature}
[MERGE:2a]
[STEP:3] @系統 {specs/features/A03-訂單/003-訂單追蹤.dsl.feature}
[FORK:3a]
  [PARALLEL:3a]
    [STEP:3a.1] @倉庫 {specs/commands/鎖定庫存.feature}
  [PARALLEL:3a]
    [STEP:3a.2] @系統 {specs/commands/發送訂單確認通知.feature}
[JOIN:3a]
[STEP:4] @系統 {specs/commands/更新訂單狀態.feature}
[FINAL]
